726479f-a.title: Queens: Douglas Avenue - 170th Street
726479f-a.text:
170-31 Douglas Avenue, north side, east of 170th Street,
showing the Shiloh Baptist Church (colored). On the right is
a Long Island Railroad power house.
P. L. Sperr  April 1, 1932
NO REPRODUCTIONS
Views 1,2
